# Per-run output directories produced by SWE-bench / Terminal-Bench wrappers.
# Run dirs are named `aura-<short-sha>-<YYYYMMDD>-<HHMMSS>`.
*/aura-*-*-*-*/
# Also catch the actual aura-<sha>-<YYYYMMDD>-<HHMMSS> shape (3 dash-separated
# segments after the `aura-` prefix) emitted by the current bin/run scripts.
*/aura-*-*-*/

# Always keep the tracked placeholders.
!**/baseline.json
!**/.gitkeep
